title: bawang_goreng
---

= Ingredients

@shallots{3}
@frying oil{}
@flour{2%tbsp}
@salt(to taste)

= Instructions

Cut @shallots{3} into thin slices.

Add @flour{2%tbsp} and a bit of @salt(to taste) to the sliced @shallots{3} and toss to coat.

Fry the coated @shallots{3} in @frying oil{} until golden and crispy, then drain on paper towels.

